title: C1_V8
description:
Back with another Space Marine Video, this time looking at the basis of a space marines specialist biology, 
Also, Voting is now open for the first chapter to get a video on VoT, please say what chapter you want to see in the comments and we'll see what gets chosen by you, the humble viewer.
Again using the new mic, I am very happy with it thus far, let me know of any Issues.

Intro Music: 
Daniel Yount - Dark Times
